title: The Power of Your Bloodline | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Power of Your Bloodline | Joel Osteen
description:
Because of what Jesus did on the cross, you don't have to live bound by anything that was passed down to you. Your new, spiritual bloodline overrides any bondage in your natural bloodline. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
